author: CNET
description: TUDUM! The box really the star of the show! 🤩 December may have started but advent calendars can be fun for even after the holidays and beyond. Let’s unbox YuMe’s 24-Day advent calendar which features fun trinkets from some of your favorite Netflix shows. #netflix #adventcalendar #holidays #tudum #bridgerton #strangerthings #witcher #onepiece #squidgame #outerbanks
title: Unboxing YuMe’s 24-Day $100 Netflix Advent Calendar: Everything You Get
